Package com.cmput301w23t40.capturetheqr

Class QRCode

java.lang.Object
com.cmput301w23t40.capturetheqr.QRCode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class QRCode extends Object implements Serializable
Each QR code object maintains the actual code's hash value, the generated code name, visualization, score. It also has a list of ScannerInfo objects, which maintains the scanners' names, the links to the pictures, the dates of scan, and a list of Comment objects, which maintains the commenters' names, the dates of the comments, and the comment contents.
